  "name": "Rockfond Rifthound Whelp",
  "desc": "A beast with monstrous blood that is capable of eroding the boundaries of the world. \"Gold\" classified them as \"Alfisol.\"<br/>They follow the encroaching abyss to devour the elements. Fortunately, there are few of them left now in this world.",
